com.tokelon.toktales.core.game.model

Interface IRectangle2i

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IRectangle2i.IMutableRectangle2i
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rectangle2iImpl

    public interface IRectangle2i
    An int precision rectangle in 2D space.

    Assumes positive Y-Axis goes DOWN and values include 0.
    That means it's origin lies in the top left corner.

    Example:
        top=0
    left=0       right=64
        bottom=32

    Width = 64
    Height = 32
    Rectangle does contain (0, 0)
    Rectangle does not contain (0, 32) or (64, 0)
